    Images:      derived from FSOCO; governed by FSOCO's terms, NOT by BRT's.

  FSOCO (Formula Student Objects in Context)
    Source: https://fsoco.github.io/fsoco-dataset/
    The images underlying BRT Cone Pose originate here. Obtain and use them
    under FSOCO's terms; cite the FSOCO paper (arXiv:2012.07139). Intended for
    Formula Student / research use -- verify the current terms before any
    commercial use.

  Note: the original MIT Driverless datasets (YOLO_Dataset.zip,
  RektNet_Dataset.zip) are no longer downloadable -- the GCS bucket returns 403
  ("The billing account for the owning project is disabled"). This is why the
  pipeline here is built on BRT Cone Pose instead.
